text: James Oatley (12 August 1845 - 17 December 1925) was an Australian cricketer. He played two first-class matches for New South Wales between 1865/66 and 1868/69. ==See also== * List of New South Wales representative cricketers ==References== ==External links== * Category:1845 births Category:1925 deaths Category:Australian cricketers Category:New South Wales cricketers Category:Cricketers from Sydney
